  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "generated" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap FRSpecimenLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"en-FRSpecimenLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcFRSpecimenLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-prelevement</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-prelevement</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.actePrelevement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.datePrelevement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.effectiveTime</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.localisationPrelevement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.targetSiteCode</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.performer</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.performer</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.echantillonPreleve</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.participant:echantillonPreleve</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.dispositifUtilise</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.participant:dispositifUtilise</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.produitUtilise</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.participant:produitUtilise</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPrelevement.dateReceptionEchantillon</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDAPrelevement.entryRelationship.act</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-prelevement</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-specimen-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.processing.procedure.coding.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.effectiveTime</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.collection.collected[x]</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.targetSiteCode</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.collection.bodySite</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.performer</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.collection.collector</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.participant:echantillonPreleve</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.type</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.participant:dispositifUtilise</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.container</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.participant:produitUtilise</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.processing.additive:Substance</td></tr><tr><td>FRCDAPrelevement.entryRelationship.act</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRSpecimenDocument.receivedTime</td></tr></table></div>"
